headline: J.D. Power Recognizes Fifth Third as No. 1 for Banking Mobile App User Satisfaction Among Regional Banks
summary: CINCINNATI - J.D. Power has recognized Fifth Third Bank as America's best mobile banking app experience among regional banks as part of its 2025 U.S. Banking Mobile App Satisfaction StudySM. Study...
